{"tid":157133,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"我真係好驚口試","createTime":"2017-03-15T09:29:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T14:11:34.000Z","uid":19552,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d89fff78bf50dd233d37e145e268762d0b09ff71","tid":157133,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T09:29:17.000Z","msg":"17號就考喇<br />\n次次校內口試都勁低分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n乘返得3,40分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小組討論果時我d同學黐線架<br />\n我未試過考一場係有人會少過三次發言(除左我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n個個爭住講 我都唔知點攝位入<br />\n有時攝到位又同時有人講<br />\n佢又冇意識讓俾我講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有point都講唔到<br />\n講到又1999咁<br />\n但係我平時好多野講<br />\n好中意係班frd前搞gag<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一諗到就快考 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 真係有心冇力"},{"pid":"4243c3077636b141791dad2d001630c31173064e","tid":157133,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T09:30:41.000Z","msg":"我油黑左兩隻牙擾敵<br />\n<br />\n仲著埋黑絲"},{"pid":"0dd8aefeaae19cb9bf2acece47fec84704c9eadb","tid":157133,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T10:34:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3e24fd18ac4a96815476bb0ad0d470664cb1756a","tid":157133,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T10:34:33.000Z","msg":"我諗住玩野同攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7adbc7538742139f1ab54ffe069a9fdf3a81a67a","tid":157133,"uid":38740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:15:31.000Z","msg":"全身aape大9個考官  希望個考官都係潮人"},{"pid":"55f8003b42979a121f582c8c2ef1e7e56dd98674","tid":157133,"uid":37733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-15T11:15:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全身aape大9個考官  希望個考官都係潮人</blockquote>